name: FSlateBrushOutlineSettings
doc: Possible options for rounded box brush image

CornerRadii: Radius in Slate Units applied to the outline at each corner. X = Top Left, Y = Top Right, Z = Bottom Right, W = Bottom Left
Color: Tinting applied to the border outline.
Width: Line width in Slate Units applied to the border outline.
bUseBrushTransparency: True if we should use the owning brush's transparency as our own *
